  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>.<br><br>This sturdy staff is hewn from polished stone, and yet floats in the hand as if it were no weight at all. It is a perfect companion to those who seek to make long trips across the wilderness.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。<br><br>虽然是使用抛光石材打造而成，但是这根结实的长杖却能够像是没有任何重量一般漂浮在你的手中。它将成为那些想要在旷野之中长途跋涉之人的最佳同伴。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">领取</span>这个多用途工具并将其加入你的收藏，或者与你当前的多用途工具进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分快速切换当前激活的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。<br><br>這根結實的棍棒由拋光的石頭鑿成，卻能飄浮在手中，彷彿根本沒有重量。對於那些想要穿越荒野進行長途旅行的人來說，它是完美的夥伴。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 中的機能選項切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
